0.3.0
	- Refactored again.
	- Configurable #configure and #configuration methods.
	- #configuration returns a Configuration object.
	- Values in Configuration are lazily evaluated if defined as a block.
	- Different symantics for module methods (not backwards compatible).

0.2.1
	- Freeze configuration after callback.
	
0.2.0
	- Automatic setters
	- Refactored

0.1.0
	- Initial release
